               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Gabra Manfas Qǝddus “Vita of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus” (fols.
                     2ra-76rb)
 II) Homily by Zenā Gabrǝʾel on Gabra Manfas Qǝddus; 4 miracles
                     in vita (fols. 76va-87va) 
 III) Taʾammǝra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus “Miracles of
                     Gabra Manfas Qǝddus”: 13 miracles (fols. 87vb-104vb)
 IV) Gadla Za-Mikāʾel
                     ʾAragāwi “Vita of Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi” (fols. 105ra-133ra)
 V) Malkǝʾa
                     Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi “Image of Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi” (fols. 133rb-136rb)
 VI)
                     Gadla Gabra Krǝstos “Vita of Gabra Krǝstos [St Alexius]” (fols. 137ra-155va)
                     (incomplete?)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
